OBLIGATORY

(Amazing masterpiece), 8k, 7-second, HDR, cinematic lighting, Amazing details, Amazing fine details, Amazing Color, Vivid color.

(Realistic, Hyperrealistic, Living person, Alive, Real, a person standing still, realistic body proportions, detailed skin texture), (The person's identity and face must remain perfectly consistent throughout the entire video),(detailed hair).

(at 1-2: A medium shot. A person with a natural, makeup-free face and simple, wet hair looks on with wide-eyed awe as a floating, intricate, metallic cube ignites before them, bathing them in a dramatic purple light).

(at 3-5: A very fast 360-degree orbital track begins. As the camera whips around, ethereal energy particles from the cube swarm them. In a seamless, overlapping sequence, their wet hair instantly dries into a futuristic braided updo, shimmering cyberpunk makeup materializes on their face, and a wave of liquid chrome transforms their clothes into a high-fashion armored suit).

(at 6-7: The orbit completes, revealing the full transformation. Their expression has now shifted from awe to one of immense power and cold confidence. They raise their open palm and a miniature, photorealistic raincloud with crackling lightning instantly forms above it).

(at 8-10: A rapid dolly zoom pushes in on their powerful face. The flashes from the tiny lightning storm illuminate their features. They look directly into the camera lens and give a slow, deliberate wink just before the final cut to black).
